CSS:
/* highlight the icon when filtered */
.k-grid th.k-filtered .k-grid-filter,
.k-grid th.k-filtered .k-header-menu.k-grid-filter svg,
.k-grid th.k-filtered .k-svg-icon {
    color: #0078d7 !important;
    fill: #0078d7 !important;
    animation: filterPulse 0.8s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}

/* animation keyframes */
@keyframes filterPulse {
    from {
        transform: scale(1);
    }
    to {
        transform: scale(1.25);
    }
}

Result:

Icon gradually grows/shrinks (smooth breathing effect)

Looks modern and clean

Doesn't distract users
